We may transmit data to companies specialized in campaign measurement.
Fraud detection:
We may transmit data to companies specialized in preventing delivering our ads on fraudulent traffic, such as non-human traffic.
Geo-location:
We may transmit the IP address of the user to companies such as digital elements which provide geo-location services.
Analytics and Audience measurement:
We transmit data to companies in order to validate the accuracy of our targeting or measure the demographic reach of our network.
