Corporate and taxation matters: to comply with our obligations under companies legislation and tax law.
Regulatory matters: to comply with our obligations to engage with regulators, such as data protection regulators.
Court Matters: a court order may require us to process or disclose personal data for a particular purpose.
Criminal matters: to comply with requests from applicable enforcement bodies to provide information in relation to a criminal investigation, as required by applicable law.
